" Remap a key sequence in insert mode to kick me out to normal
" mode. This makes it so this key sequence can never be typed
" again in insert mode, so it has to be unique.
inoremap jj <esc>
inoremap jJ <esc>
inoremap Jj <esc>
inoremap JJ <esc>
inoremap jk <esc>
inoremap jK <esc>
inoremap Jk <esc>
inoremap JK <esc>

